00:29:39.160 --> 00:29:40.920
Nawa'y ang aking Panginoon at si Xiao Yao

00:29:40.920 --> 00:29:41.270
sabay-sabay na tumanda nang may pagkakaisa,

00:29:41.270 --> 00:29:42.200
